What you need to know:  The hosts, who are coached by former Harambee Stars and Gor Mahia defender Tobias Ochola beat Makerere University 2-1 in the tough semi-final, where both sides were reduced to 10 menKU will Friday square it out with 2008 champions Makerere University of Business Studies (MUBS) in the finalMUBS, who last lifted the title in 2008 thrashed Ghana's University of Development Studies (UDS) 3-0 in the other men's semi-final